collection.name: "MOAR" by Joan Cornella
collection.description: ** MOAR by Joan Cornellà ** is an unusual mansion in the metaverse proudly presented by FWENCLUB, where 5,555 creatures with their souls minted with the ERC721 blockchain as NFTs. Each of these "peacefully-living-together" humans, cyborgs or even zombies, is unique, hand-drawn by Spanish artist Joan Cornellà using over 200 unique attributes. You may even find shops, games, virtual exhibitions … and MOAR!
